.TH "RTCTRANSPORTSTATS.BYTESSENT" "3JS" "June 24, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
RTCTransportStats.bytesSent \- RTCTransportStats: bytesSent property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]bytesSent\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]RTCTransportStats\f[R] dictionary indicates the total number of
payload bytes sent on this transport.
.PP
Only data bytes are counted; overhead such as padding, headers, and so
on are not included in this count.
.SH VALUE
A positive integer indicating the number of sent payload bytes.
